{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T03:31:09.178Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on my search results, I cannot find the exact official Anthropic documentation page titled \"Reasoning in Practice\" with a specific section called \"When to Use Reasoning\" containing \"Reasoning Use Cases.\" However, I can provide you with a comprehensive explanation based on the available information about Claude's reasoning capabilities and when to use them."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Reasoning Use Cases in Claude's \"When to Use Reasoning\""}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What it is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reasoning Use Cases"},{"type":"text","text":" refer to the specific types of tasks and problems where Claude's extended thinking/reasoning mode provides significant value over standard responses. These are scenarios where step-by-step logical thinking, multi-stage analysis, and careful consideration of trade-offs matter more than speed."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why it matters"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Reasoning models like Claude 3.7 Sonnet (the first hybrid reasoning model) and newer Claude Opus/Sonnet 4.x models with extended thinking can solve complex problems that regular completion models fail at. For example, reasoning models showed "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"+44% improvement on hard algorithm problems"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"+37% on math proofs"},{"type":"text","text":" compared to regular LLMs."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Reasoning Use Cases"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use Case"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why Reasoning Helps"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Complex mathematical problems"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Multi-step calculations require verifying intermediate results"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Logical reasoning & puzzles"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Needs systematic deduction rather than pattern prediction"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Complex algorithmic problems"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Requires multi-step derivation; e.g., implementing LFU cache with O(1) operations"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Math problems & proofs"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"o3 reached PhD-level on GPQA math benchmark; improvements in physics/chemistry/engineering"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Bug location (complex)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Must analyze call chains and multi-module interactions; reasoning models track root cause better"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Deep code review"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Needs to understand architecture and find potential issues"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Technical architecture decisions"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Requires evaluating trade-offs and catching edge cases"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Business decisions & strategic planning"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Reasoning process is as crucial as final outcome"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Multi-step planning"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Chains multiple decisions with reasoning between steps"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Agentic tool use with branches"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Reason about tool results before deciding next action"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Deep analysis of long documents"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Claude handles ~200K tokens; excellent for contracts, reports, legal documents"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Research & analysis"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Multi-variable business impact assessment, predictive escalation modeling"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When NOT to Use Reasoning"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use Case"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Reason to Skip"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Simple translation, formatting"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Regular LLM sufficient; faster, cheaper"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Chat conversations"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"High API latency doesn't fit chat interfaces"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Summaries"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Standard mode works well"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Classification"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pattern-based; reasoning adds unnecessary cost"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Simple extraction"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Regular LLM sufficient"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Real-time interaction"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Reasoning models are 10-100x more expensive"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"High-frequency calls"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cost explosion; use on things that matter"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How it works"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When extended thinking is enabled:\n1. Claude creates "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" content blocks where it outputs internal reasoning step-by-step\n2. It incorporates insights from this reasoning before crafting the final response\n3. The API returns "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"thinking"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks followed by "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" blocks\n4. For Claude 4 models, you get summarized thinking (not full verbose reasoning) by default"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Practical implementation"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"python"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"response = client.messages.create(\n    model=\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\n    max_tokens=16000,\n    thinking={\"type\": \"enabled\", \"budget_tokens\": 10000},  # 16k+ for complex tasks\n    messages=[{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"Your complex problem here\"}]\n)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Best practices:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- Start with minimum budget (1,024 tokens), increase incrementally\n- Use 16k+ tokens for complex tasks\n- For budgets above 32k, use batch processing\n- Provide ample context—reasoning models are \"context hungry\"\n- Use phased prompts: analysis → synthesis → recommendation\n- Include explicit decision criteria to guide judgments"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Reasoning isn't \"smarter\""},{"type":"text","text":"—it's LLMs that spend more time (test-time compute) to get more accurate answers"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Value"},{"type":"text","text":": Improves success rate on \"think-before-answer\" tasks from 30-50% to 70-80%"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cost tradeoff"},{"type":"text","text":": 10-100x more expensive than regular LLMs"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Use as specialized tool"},{"type":"text","text":": For \"hard problems,\" not daily workhorses"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude's strength"},{"type":"text","text":": Depth over speed; use for situations requiring genuine thought rather than pattern recognition"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The question isn't \"should I use a reasoning model?\" but rather \"how much thinking do I want this call to do?\"."}]}]}}
